purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test names associated with detecting the presence of E. coli Shiga Toxin or Shiga-like Toxin by immunoassay),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: component: Escherichia coli shiga-like or Escherichia coli shiga toxin;  

LOINC search:  'Escherichia coli shiga toxin immunoassay -panel -culture ';  

Plus:  
- 53946-0  Escherichia coli shiga-like toxin identified in Unspecified specimen;  
- 16283-4  Escherichia coli verotoxin [Presence] in Unspecified specimen;  
- 6576-3	Escherichia coli verotoxin 2 [Presence] in Stool;  
- 6574-8	Escherichia coli verotoxin 1 [Presence] in Stool;),(Exclusion Criteria: verotoxin Ab tests)
